comment:
Maybe her legal team is not allowing things to come out because they know it will backfire on her but instead maybe the real reason is because she is impossible to work with, advise and insists on things that they know shouldn‚Äôt be brought up.  

No one knows what truly goes on behind closed doors except for the people involved. I don‚Äôt want to believe anything she says and I haven‚Äôt. However I have to add that I personally have known of some relationships that have been abusive and involved people who had never been violent with any partner or any person ever before. Some people bring out the worst in each other. Unfortunately some people will stay in situations like that because the flip side of the abuse is also very passionate. 

What we can say with certainty is that she ruined him. The photos of him after the divorce were very worrisome. He did not look healthy at all. She destroyed his career, his reputation and became the straw that broke the camels back in regards to his finances as well. Another thing we can say for certain is that her greatest role was being his wife. She will always be known and famous for their divorce and for ruining the amazing Johnny Depp. Yet he is known internationally for so many amazing roles. He had more fame at the age she was when she landed her first movie than she will ever have in her lifetime. There are so many sharks in Hollywood that are out for themselves and to suck the finances out of anyone famous that they can get close to. I can‚Äôt help but to feel she belongs in that category. I wouldn‚Äôt be surprised if it came out that this was her plan all along. I‚Äôve seen enough of her roles to be able to say that without him she would‚Äôve never earned the fame she has now or the perks and lifestyle he was able to give her off of her merits alone. She could never reach that kind of status without him. Honestly this entire saga is sad and disgusting. We‚Äôve all seen how hard it is for celebrities to keep things private but she flat out launched a campaign of character assassination against him. She wanted everything that could be used against him to become public knowledge. That alone says a lot about her character in my opinion.
